{"tid":1520103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人再係咁真係End Game","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T18:48:17.000Z","uid":42960,"like":63,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"abff71cb2e3d02db461c5cdc5ed71abcda7495a8","tid":1520103,"uid":42960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"Sorry，我係標題黨<br />\n但大家再好似之前咁真係遲早End Game<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBesMXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBesMXB.jpg&h=e4c8fcfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家聽日瞓醒心態要轉<br />\n無論點都<span style=\"color: red;\">面向前方</span><br />\n對方慢慢向前行十步<br />\n我哋先可<span style=\"color: red;\">面向</span>對方向後十步<br />\n對方真係全速跑過嚟時<br />\n先可以連同身邊人一排排咁退<br />\n一個不能少<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話速龍個啲出嚟好危險<br />\n我會話佢哋都咁快點會反應得切<br />\n一於唔好畀反應，一齊唔退一齊面對面向佢哋<br />\n佢哋一隊人就算打得過我哋第一排<br />\n但第二三四五六排唔退唔怕嘅話<br />\n我想問邊一邊強大啲？<br />\n<br />\nBe Water 係重要，但救人同齊心一致向外都同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n睇多次張相，記住我哋可以錯，但記住要改<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBesMXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBesMXB.jpg&h=e4c8fcfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4dc8278aaf755fd4e3d96d8bde84201c18796a6d","tid":1520103,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=e0eb6cc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=89eb3965\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=7eebd4a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"7124289d2d189b133bc7ab783a97a552c3f7d0e3","tid":1520103,"uid":42960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"因為有fd mon我account<br />\n所以成個運動無開過post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罰自己自推20次"},{"pid":"20c9e88127d696c2174386e88a493250090b35bd","tid":1520103,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d619ba8796ae5f7f175757dbd8eb2add60b00303","tid":1520103,"uid":42960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"多啲鼓勵同提醒身邊人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">面向前方</span><br />\n少少動作足以改變一切"},{"pid":"826cbac52173aafc7a83d3ffa92dc17199156a66","tid":1520103,"uid":42960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"ca76d7eab8da3218bf1bc36eb8be59f973182c4c","tid":1520103,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7124289d2d189b133bc7ab783a97a552c3f7d0e3","tid":1520103,"uid":42960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"因為有fd mon我account<br />\n所以成個運動無開過post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罰自己自推20次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"Mon都要開post 俾佢地知呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d992f62dbe31768df95d8a5423bd17f0515248e6","tid":1520103,"uid":42960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca76d7eab8da3218bf1bc36eb8be59f973182c4c","tid":1520103,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{